title: Update on road accident involving teenage girl in Morningside (New Zealand Police)
text: ( Source : New Zealand Police ) Auckland City Police say their Invesigations are continuing into a road accident in Morningside last Thursday where a 14-year-old girl was struck by a vehicle. Road Policing Manager, Inspector Andy King said
